**Example in TypeScript** (from [4]):
```typescript
let response = await client.beta.conversations.start({
    model: "mistral-medium-latest",
    inputs:[{role: "user", content:"Who is Albert Einstein?"}]
});
```

This is also supported in the documentation's tip ([1]):
> *"You can start and continue conversations without creating Agents... you can use the `model` parameter instead of `agent_id`."*

